To build:

  west build -b cdns_swerv/s400/whisper samples/hello_world/

To Run and debug:

  Set the following environment varibles:
    export WHISPER_BASE=<dir to swerv-sw-package-*>
    export WHISPER_BIN=${WHISPER_BASE}/whisper/board/swerv400/whisper

  Run via west:
    west build -b cdns_swerv/s400/whisper samples/hello_world/ -t run

  Debug via west:
    Start debug server:
      west build -b cdns_swerv/s400/whisper samples/hello_world/ -t debugserver

    Use GDB to connect to port 1234

To Run manually under swerv-sw-package-SA-2023.2-debian/ :

  whisper/board/swerv400/whisper /tmp/build/zephyr/zephyr.elf --raw \
          --configfile riscv-fw-infrastructure/firmware/board/whisper/whisper_swerv400.json

To Debug manually:

  whisper/board/swerv400/whisper /tmp/build/zephyr/zephyr.elf --raw \
          --gdb --gdb-tcp-port 1234 \
          --configfile riscv-fw-infrastructure/firmware/board/whisper/whisper_swerv400.json
